      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 11 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 11 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九，拔茅茹以其彙，征吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, suggests the idea of grass pulled up, and bringing with it other stalks with whose roots it is connected. Advance (on the part of its subject) will be fortunate.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="yijing-011-tai__alignment-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">yijing</prop>
