      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 11 九二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 11 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二，包荒。用馮河，不遐遺；朋亡。得尚于中行。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows one who can bear with the uncultivated, will cross the He without a boat, does not forget the distant, and has no (selfish) friendships. Thus does he prove himself acting in accordance with the course of the due Mean.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="yijing-011-tai__alignment-004">
      <prop type="x-work-id">yijing</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">yijing-011-tai</prop>
