      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 11 六五</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 11 六五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五，帝乙歸妹，以祉，元吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth six, divided, reminds us of (king) Di-yi's (rule about the) marriage of his younger sister. By such a course there is happiness and there will be great good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
