      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 11 上六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 11 上六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上六，城復于隍，勿用師，自邑告命，貞吝。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The sixth six, divided, shows us the city wall returned into the moat. It is not the time to use the army. (The subject of the line) may, indeed, announce his orders to the people of his own city; but however correct and firm he may be, he will have cause for regret.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
